title: Luther seizoen 4
description:
S4, Ep1
15 Dec. 2015
Episode #4.1
While on a leave of absence, Luther is suddenly dragged back into his former life in London to battle the demons of his past and to stop a cannibal serial killer.
 
Episode #4.2
